According to a report by Intel Market Research, the global Packaged Salad Market was valued at USD 5.69 billion in 2025 and is projected to grow from USD 6.12 billion in 2026 to USD 9.77 billion by 2034, registering a CAGR of 8.2% during the forecast period. The market is witnessing strong momentum as consumers increasingly seek convenient, nutritious, and ready-to-eat meal solutions that fit busy lifestyles. Growing health awareness, the rising popularity of plant-based diets, and continuous expansion of supermarket and online grocery channels are further supporting market growth worldwide.
